Legal Notice for Web Scraping:
This software is designed to work only with websites that explicitly allow 
scraping, such as demo sites created for educational purposes. Users are 
responsible for ensuring compliance with:

1. Website Terms of Service
2. robots.txt files
3. Local and international laws regarding data collection
4. Rate limiting and ethical scraping practices

The included demo sites (books.toscrape.com, quotes.toscrape.com) are 
specifically designed for scraping practice and are legal to use for 
educational and testing purposes.